e":"August 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the most admired ally of mine is a believer of little wealth, given to prayer, who has been excellent in the worship of his Lord and has obeyed Him in secret, who was obscure among people for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34167,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/30\/acts-of-worship-spoiled\/","url_meta":{"origin":43597,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Worship: Acts of worship spoiled by insincerity and sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne who fasts might only acquire hunger and thirst from his fasting. One who stands for prayer might only acquire fatigue from his prayer.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 13413 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19490,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/15\/no-reward-insincere-worship\/","url_meta":{"origin":43597,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Worship: They get no reward for insincere worship","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 15, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne might fast but he gets nothing from his fast except hunger. One might pray at night but he gets nothing from his prayer except fatigue.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1690 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5514,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/25\/virtue-salat-first-row-jamaah\/","url_meta":{"origin":43597,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Virtue of praying in first row of congregation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 25, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ubay ibn Ka\u2019b reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, the first row of prayer resembles the rows of angels. If you knew its virtue, you would compete for it. The prayer of a man with another man is more purifying than his prayer\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4362,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/07\/worship-jihad-ten-nights-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":43597,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: The Prophet strives in last ten nights","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When the last ten nights of Ramadan arrived, the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would tighten his belt, spend the night in worship, and awaken his family. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2024, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1174 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7645,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/04\/best-nalf-salat-house\/","url_meta":{"origin":43597,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Best voluntary prayer offered at home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Thabit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"O people, perform prayer in your houses, for the best prayer of a man is in his house, except for the prescribed prayers.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 731 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/43597","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"ht